{"tid":1275693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢醒咗 睇到立場姐姐訪問喊左","createTime":"2019-07-01T21:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:54:39.000Z","uid":238169,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49ec58e71d6d9381f609a02ff98fe49e1c506248","tid":1275693,"uid":238169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:45:00.000Z","msg":"第一次開post<br />\n<br />\n我想講對唔住，因為我有包袱、細膽限制左我行動。我見到入面嘅人比我更加勇敢，尤其見到一班女仔咁落力我真係自愧不如。<br />\n<br />\n今日我單丁去發夢，出黎前已經好猶疑去唔去好。其實我好驚又無照應，過程好迷惘。雖然我去咗，但我全程都畏首畏尾，好驚比人影到，因為我無同屋企人講，好驚比佢地發現。<br />\n<br />\n但係我睇完個訪問之後，雖然我一個人去有時覺得迷惘、無助、驚，但我無後悔。因為我見到有一班好有愛既香港人，就算驚都唔怕。大家一齊黎就要一齊走，我地唔放棄每一個人。<br />\n<br />\n如果之後再要發夢，我唔會再猶豫，就算我幾驚都好又係一個人去都好，我都會出黎，因為我前面已經有一班勇敢嘅義士。我就算驚唔敢上前，我都要做佢地後盾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學訪問個妹妹咁講：「個個人都好驚，但仲驚聽日見唔到佢地。」<br />\n<br />\n而我想講多句之後我地仲要一齊守護香港！<br />\n<br />\n「因為我地最驚既係香港唔再係香港！」<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要堅持落去，一個都不能少。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，齊上齊落。</span></span>"},{"pid":"febab062f48722b751e28f65067e70442f9d9a19","tid":1275693,"uid":266706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:48:55.000Z","msg":"大家加油!"},{"pid":"ae68621c0c66b5c2a314d061dbc0348ac3c69924","tid":1275693,"uid":189417,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:51:37.000Z","msg":"仲玩分化. 今日&quot;一齊走&quot;單嘢簡直係人性嘅光輝<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275458</a><br />\n<br />\n一齊走 係呢世人聽過最好聽嘅說話  - 節錄一個香港人留言 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed493f095e5f4f32e7201d645afd30942ed35ee","tid":1275693,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:51:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">得閒唔該幫手推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【廣傳】所有出現過喺現場嘅義士，見到呢個post 即刻更改Facebook私隱設定，尤其係相！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275626</a></span>"},{"pid":"62861e38e94aa1b3c98c833c97ffcb14d451a9a1","tid":1275693,"uid":182575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:52:23.000Z","msg":"又多一個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2b348e36705bbde8ee7a43161c68e40a828d2f","tid":1275693,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:01:59.000Z","msg":"香港人真心好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bda35f51c96a2f09997cc81678b96e88fb949c","tid":1275693,"uid":238169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62861e38e94aa1b3c98c833c97ffcb14d451a9a1","tid":1275693,"uid":182575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:52:23.000Z","msg":"又多一個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:43:52.000Z","msg":"手足唔怕多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46a811b4353fa8bd1c6e8157ad0b3c6ea1bac68","tid":1275693,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4231597bf050701ee362ede6b93138427fbdb726","tid":1275693,"uid":213048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:03:00.000Z","msg":"唔緊要架，每個人都會有自己嘅包袱，但鍵盤戰士都可以係我地嘅戰友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c58da690267b0befad